{"tid":2108151,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"車仔Kepa＋轉會費斟Oblak？","createTime":"2020-07-14T10:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T13:15:11.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"790fbb33871f1ad2859231b570aa86e7eaae5cf9","tid":2108151,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:32:32.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】車路士為改善後防，有意引入馬德里體育會門神奧比勒，據報球會希望以門將艾利沙巴拿加另加轉會費為交易條件。<br />\n<br />\n車路士之前3季聯賽失球不超過40球，但今季35場已失掉49球，看來領隊林柏特對門將艾利沙巴拿加（Kepa Arrizabalaga）失去耐性，而據《鏡報》報道，藍軍鎖定馬體會的奧比勒（Jan Oblak）為目標。據悉車路士希望以艾利沙巴拿加再加轉會費，作為交易奧比勒的條件。<br />\n<br />\n艾利沙巴拿加2018年以8000萬歐元全球最高守門員轉會費加盟車路士，該名25歲西班牙門將今季聯賽上陣31場失42球，場均失1.35球，當中只有7場保持清白身。反觀27歲斯洛文尼亞門將奧比勒，今季為馬體會於聯賽披甲36場僅失26球，當中16戰保持不失球。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提是，馬體會去年跟副隊長奧比勒續約至2023年，合約中包括1.3億歐元的買斷條款。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"d1fa7f41f49c4dadf46c25fd3775a263485f0c3b","tid":2108151,"uid":153400,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/16a8c2d0650691cc684488e84832dc08/tenor.gif?itemid=15485931\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F16a8c2d0650691cc684488e84832dc08%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D15485931&h=e83cc1fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a4a303e29475030d41549af9f1181a7f51468ca","tid":2108151,"uid":300938,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d1fa7f41f49c4dadf46c25fd3775a263485f0c3b","tid":2108151,"uid":153400,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/16a8c2d0650691cc684488e84832dc08/tenor.gif?itemid=15485931\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F16a8c2d0650691cc684488e84832dc08%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D15485931&h=e83cc1fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:41:14.000Z","msg":"薛耶治嚟到會唔會面左左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3402c2